Class CreatePDFParams

java.lang.Object
com.adobe.pdfservices.operation.pdfjobs.params.createpdf.CreatePDFParams
All Implemented Interfaces:
PDFServicesJobParams
Direct Known Subclasses:
CreatePDFFromExcelParams, CreatePDFFromPPTParams, CreatePDFFromWordParams
public abstract class CreatePDFParams extends Object implements PDFServicesJobParams
Marker base class for CreatePDFJob params. The factory methods within this class can be used to create instances of params classes corresponding to the source media type.
